{
  "id": "nce2-l53",
  "title": "Lesson 53: Hot Snake",
  "audio": "/audio/nce2/53ÔºçHot Snake.mp3",
  "image": "/images/coming-soon.png",
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "intro_1",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "What caused the fire?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 10.58,
      "endTime": 14.43
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "At last firemen have put out a big forest fire in California.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 14.44,
      "endTime": 21.1
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Since then, they have been trying to find out how the fire began.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 21.11,
      "endTime": 27.62
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Forest fires are often caused by broken glass or by cigarette ends which people carelessly throw away.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 27.63,
      "endTime": 37.95
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Yesterday the firemen examined the ground carefully,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 37.96,
      "endTime": 42.31
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "but were not able to find any broken glass.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 42.32,
      "endTime": 46.79
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "They were also quite sure that a cigarette end did not start the fire.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 46.8,
      "endTime": 53
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "This morning, however, a firemen accidentally discovered the cause.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 53.01,
      "endTime": 59.37
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "He noticed the remains of a snake which was wound round the electric wires of a 16, 000-volt power line.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 59.38,
      "endTime": 69.97
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "In this way, he was able to solve the mystery.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 69.98,
      "endTime": 74.64
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The explanation was simple but very unusual.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 74.65,
      "endTime": 80.02
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "A bird had snatched up the snake from the ground and then dropped it on to the wires.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 80.03,
      "endTime": 87.82
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The snake then wound itself round the wires.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 87.83,
      "endTime": 91.73
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "When it did so, it sent sparks down to the ground and these immediately started a fire.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 91.74,
      "endTime": 96.74
    }
  ]
}